webelement interface---it is an interface of slenium arcticter which 14 abstract method to perform action on any web element or to  retrive information from any web elment 


what is web element---any thing present on the web page is called as webelement 
ex--textfield ,radio button cheak box ,button ,normal text,link text,

1 click
2 send key
